snippet.title: Industria 2 | Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
INDUSTRIA 2 is a narrative FPS adventure about a woman stranded in a parallel dimension. Explore, scavenge and fight your way through a mysterious boreal landscape consumed by an ever-hungry artificial intelligence to find a way home. 

Wishlist now!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2154070/INDUSTRIA_2
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/p/industria-2-a1232a
GoG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/industria_2
